rComments: Great prof all around! Made a boring and tough subject engaging. Takes special care to make sure every student has a chance to succeed. Stats experiments he does in his class are delightful.
He is really a good professor.

Pavel tries hard, but he gives dumb examples in class and wastes time.  His accent can be difficult to understand.  If you don't get the material, he'll tell you that you need to teach yourselves the material, an that, he's not here to teach but to focus on research.   It would be nice if he can do both of these well.
Makes lectures fairly interesting for the subject matter.
GREAT professor. Helpful, intends for you to do well, interested in your wellbeing.
